<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Knolann Caelestis</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-11 21:32:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Correct me if I'm wrong here: the length of fear/charm spells is affected by Charisma, but it works two ways. Enchanters/Bards like high Charisma, but a Shadowknight with terrible Charisma would notice a benefit in their fear type spells. Conclusion: this is a nice Shadowknight mask, and perhaps something you should switch out to before casting a fear spell.<BR>
<BR>
-Knolann Caelestis, a guy who has just created a SK and is looking to learn more about the class...</font></td></tr></table>
